data.description: Finally the true definition of "House Hacking"... This amazing must see property already comes with a tenant so you'll have instant savings on the mortgage. Unit 1 can be considered a split unit as the basement allows for additional living space along with a half bath  and tall ceilings. The main floor of unit 1 has an ensuite bath, access to the garage and the deck. Plus, making this unit even sweeter it was renovated in August to its current state. The renovation included new windows, the refinishing of these absolutely beautiful parquet floors, doors, updated kitchen 36" cabinets and granite countertops, updated spa-like bathroom with Bluetooth sound. The second floor unit is a 1 bedroom unit that contains plenty of space with a large living room and bedroom. Property is close and accessible to everything... Nightlife, dining, shopping, local universities, schools, transportation, and major roadways. This property won't last.
